---
title: Steakhouse Bison Cheeseburgers with Mushroom Gravy and Spiced Potato Wedges
description: Familiar steakhouse flavours of mushroom gravy and Montreal Steak Spice amp up this weeknight cheeseburger. Dunk the golden roasted potatoes into the zesty mayo for a texture-taste sensation!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steakhouse-bison-cheeseburgers-5b5a3cea.jpg
